Notes: This column appears to contain unique identifiers for each problem condition, making 'hasIdentifier' the most semantically appropriate property.
The 'patient_id' directly references the patient associated with the problem condition, aligning with the 'hasPatient' relationship.
Diagnosis codes are best mapped to the 'Code' entity to represent coded data accurately.
Timestamp data is best mapped directly to the 'hasDateTime' property with datatype 'dateTime'.
Organization code logically maps to the data provider institute responsible for the record.
Organization name is a straightforward string label, mapped via 'hasName'.
